text: Návrh zasedacího pořádku poslanců v jednacím sále Poslanecké sněmovny
translation-cs: Proposal for a sitting order of Members in the Chamber of Deputies' Chamber of Deputies
translation-sla: Draft meeting order of Members in the Chamber of Procedure of the Chamber of Members
translation-zlw: Proposal for a meeting order of Members in the Chamber of Deputies

text: Podle § 52 odst. 1 našeho jednacího řádu Poslanecká sněmovna schvaluje zasedací pořádek poslanců v jednacím sále Poslanecké sněmovny a byl vám rozdán návrh tak, jak se na něm dohodly jednotlivé poslanecké kluby.
translation-cs: According to Article 52 (2) (a) of the basic Regulation, the Commission considers that the aid is compatible with the internal market under Article 107 (3) (c) of the Treaty on the Functioning of the European Union and Article 108 (3) of the Treaty on the Functioning of the European Union. 1 of our Rules of Procedure The Chamber of Deputies approves the sitting arrangements of Members in the Chamber of Deputies' Chamber of Deputies' Chamber of Deputies' Chamber of Deputies' Chamber of Deputies' Chamber of Deputies' Chamber of Deputies, and a proposal has been given to you as agreed upon by the various Members' Clubs.
translation-sla: According to Paragraph 52(a) 1 of our Rules of Procedure, the Chamber of Parliament approves the meeting order of Members in the Chamber of Procedure of the Chamber of Members and you have been presented with a proposal as agreed upon by individual parliamentary clubs.
translation-zlw: According to Article 52(2) of CRR, the amount of assigned revenue in accordance with Article 21(3) of the Financial Regulation is estimated at EUR 1000000. 1 of our Rules of Procedure The Chamber of Deputies approves the meetings of Members in the Chamber of Deputies and the proposal has been distributed to you as agreed by the various Members' Clubs.

text: Já bych k této věci otevřel rozpravu.
translation-cs: I would like to open a debate on this matter.
translation-sla: I'd open a debate on this.
translation-zlw: I would open a debate on this.

text: Pan poslanec a předseda klubu ODS Zbyněk Stanjura.
translation-cs: Member and Chairman of the ODS Club Zbyněk Stanjura.
translation-sla: Member of the Council and President of the ODS Zbyniek Stanjura.
translation-zlw: Member and Chairman of ODS Zbyněk Stanjur.

text: Omlouvám se, my navrhujeme ještě v rámci našich míst tři změny.
translation-cs: I'm sorry, we're still proposing three changes within our seats.

translation-cs: So I would read them as an amendment.

text: To znamená konkrétně: na místě 162 místo pana poslance Zahradníka pan poslanec Svoboda, na místě 163 místo pana poslance Pospíšila pan poslanec Zahradník a na místě 167 místo pana poslance Svobody pan poslanec Pospíšil.

text: Děkuju a omlouvám se za komplikaci, že jsme to na poslední chvilku změnili.

text: Dále nikoho přihlášeného nevidím, takže rozpravu končím.

text: Přednesl bych tedy návrh usnesení s tím, že budeme hlasovat o modifikaci oné tabulky ve znění návrhu pana poslance Stanjury, pokud to nikdo nezpochybňuje a nebude chtít zvlášť hlasovat o tom přesazování.

text: Myslím si, že je to dohoda v rámci klubu ODS a není třeba to podrobovat hlasování.
translation-cs: I think that this is an agreement within the ODS and there is no need to put it to the vote.

text: Usnesení by znělo: "Poslanecká sněmovna schvaluje zasedací pořádek poslanců v jednacím sále Poslanecké sněmovny podle předloženého návrhu ve znění pozměňovacího návrhu pana poslance Stanjury."
translation-cs: The resolution would read: 'The Chamber of Deputies approves the sitting order of Members in the Chamber of Deputies' Chamber of Deputies in accordance with the proposal tabled, as amended by Mr Stanjura's amendment.'
translation-sla: The resolution would read: "The Parliament of the Member States shall approve the meeting order of Members in the Chamber of Procedure of the Chamber of the Parliament in accordance with the proposal tabled as amended by Mr Stanjura's amendment."
translation-zlw: The resolution would be: "The Chamber of Deputies approves the meeting order of Members in the Chamber of Deputies in accordance with the proposal tabled, as amended by Mr Stanjura's amendment."
